=====================================
          FULL SYMBOL LIST
=====================================


 SYMBOL  |       DESCRIPTION
---------|-------------------------------
 ' '     | Walk Space
 /       | Non-Existing Untouchable Land
 \       | Not-Apart-Of-Map
 &       | Barrier
 #       | Wall
 %       | Waterfall (Barrier/Wall [NON-INTERACTIVE])
 =       | Waterfall (Barrier/Object [INTERACTIVE])
 @       | Almond Water Supply
 :       | Climbable Wall
 |       | Climbable Object
 !       | Interactive Object
 ?       | Object Chest
 *       | User Chest
 +       | Door
 -       | Non-Interactive Door
 [       | Window (Start)
 .       | Window (Middle)
 ]       | Window (End)
 {       | Break-in-Ground (Start)
 _       | Break-in-Ground (Middle)
 }       | Break-in-Ground (End)
 X       | Boss Door
 D       | Boss Spawner
 M       | Mini-Boss Spawner
 T       | Trap
 W       | Weapon
 A       | Armor
 S       | Skill
 E       | Enemy
 Y       | Enemy Encampment
 O       | Mini-Boss Group
 G       | Boss Group
 C       | Camp (NPCs)
 Z       | Safe Zone
 L       | Ladder Way (Up/Down)
 H       | Hole (Down Only)
 R       | Rope (Up Only)
 Q       | Teleporter Home
 I       | Teleporter Instance (Waypoint)
 P       | Puzzle Piece
 V       | Vending Unit
 B       | Boat
 ~       | Water (Deadly [BOAT ONLY])
 ,       | Water (Swimable [SKILL NEEDED])
 --      | Properties Selector

=====================================
  Use symbols to build maps visually.
=====================================
